WEBVTT

00:04.471 --> 00:05.339 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Good evening. I'm
Gwen Ifill.

00:05.439 --> 00:06.506 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And I'm Judy
Woodruff.

00:06.607 --> 00:08.408 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: On the "NewsHour"
tonight:

00:08.508 --> 00:11.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES COMEY, FBI Director: We
hope that our
fellow Americans will not let
fear become

00:11.979 --> 00:13.647 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
disabling.

00:13.747 --> 00:17.618 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: A nation in mourning
searches
for answers. At least 49
innocent people are

00:17.718 --> 00:24.558 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
dead and 53 wounded in the worst
mass shooting
in modern American history --
how a gay Orlando

00:24.658 --> 00:27.027 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
