tragedy.

00:27.127 --> 00:31.231 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Here at this
center, which
is the hub of the LGBT community
in Orlando,

00:31.331 --> 00:35.836 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
there is a mixture of sadness,
and anger,
and strength in the face of this
horrendous

00:35.936 --> 00:37.838 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
act.

00:37.938 --> 00:41.642 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Also ahead:
Presidential candidates
weigh in with stark differences
-- how the

00:41.742 --> 00:46.179 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
