will alter the
campaign going forward.

00:46.280 --> 00:52.152 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And we examine how
Orlando is
sparking a national debate on
gun control

00:52.252 --> 00:53.787 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
