NewsHour."

01:00.027 --> 01:02.496 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
(BREAK)

01:02.596 --> 01:14.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Orlando, a city that
evokes theme
parks and good times, now also a
blood-stained

01:14.675 --> 01:21.214 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
entry in American history, 49
people, plus
the killer, slain at a gay
nightclub. Sunday's

01:21.315 --> 01:26.486 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
massacre led today to a search
for motive
and for missed signals.

01:26.586 --> 01:28.722 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
William Brangham begins our
coverage in Orlando.

01:28.822 --> 01:32.826 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: There was
relative calm
outside the Pulse nightclub this
morning,

01:32.926 --> 01:39.967 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a far remove from the chaos of
24 hours earlier.
Amateur video captured the
terror, gunshots

01:40.067 --> 01:43.637 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
shattering the party atmosphere
inside the
club.

01:43.737 --> 01:49.977 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The man firing the shots was
29-year-old Omar
Mateen, ultimately killed by a
SWAT team inside.

01:50.077 --> 01:52.546 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Police said today they have no
regrets about
storming the club.

01:52.646 --> 01:55.782 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN MINA, Orlando, Florida,
Police Chief:
Based on information we received
from the

01:55.882 --> 02:04.324 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
suspect, and from the hostages,
and people
inside, we believed further loss
of life was

02:04.424 --> 02:09.796 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
imminent. I made the decision to
commence
the rescue operation and do the
explosive

02:09.896 --> 02:11.665 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
breach.

02:11.765 --> 02:14.468 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: During the
attack, Mateen
called 911 dispatchers and
pledged loyalty

02:14.568 --> 02:16.536 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to the Islamic State.

02:16.636 --> 02:24.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Today, ISIS radio released an
audio statement
calling him a soldier of the
caliphate. And

02:24.311 --> 02:28.682 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
officials in Saudi Arabia
confirmed he'd visited
their country twice for
pilgrimages.

02:28.782 --> 02:33.553 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, in Washington, FBI Director
James Comey
said there's every reason to
think Mateen

02:33.653 --> 02:35.389 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
acted on his own.

02:35.489 --> 02:39.292 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES COMEY, FBI Director: There
are strong
indications of radicalization by
this killer

02:39.393 --> 02:45.565 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and of potential inspiration by
foreign terrorist
organizations. So far, we see no
indication

02:45.665 --> 02:50.537 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that this was a plot directed
from outside
the United States, and we see no
indication

02:50.637 --> 02:52.572 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that he was part of any kind of
network.

02:52.672 --> 02:56.910 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: The FBI had
investigated
Mateen on suspicions of
terrorist sympathies,

02:57.010 --> 03:00.347 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
but the results were
inconclusive, and Comey
defended his agents' work.

03:00.447 --> 03:06.420 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES COMEY: Our investigation
involved introducing
confidential sources to him,
recording conversations

03:06.520 --> 03:13.193 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
with him, following him,
reviewing transactional
records from his communications,
and searching

03:13.293 --> 03:18.165 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
all government holdings for any
possible connections,
any possible derogatory
information.

03:18.265 --> 03:22.936 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: As
investigators now searched
the gunman's home in Fort
Pierce, Florida,

03:23.036 --> 03:28.241 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
sharply differing images of him
have emerged.
His Afghan-born father
apologized again today

03:28.341 --> 03:30.210 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to the victims.

03:30.310 --> 03:34.047 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And in a Facebook video,
speaking in Dari,
he reflected on his son and the
crime he committed.

03:34.147 --> 03:40.787 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEDDIQUE MIR MATEEN, Father of
Omar Mateen:
My son Omar a good son and
educated person.

03:40.887 --> 03:45.092 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I don't know what caused him to
do it. I don't
know what happened. And I didn't
know he had

03:45.192 --> 03:50.931 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
hatred. The issue of
homosexuality and punishment
belongs to God. It doesn't
belong to a servant

03:51.031 --> 03:52.866 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
of Allah

03:52.966 --> 03:56.436 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But Mateen's
ex-wife painted
a starkly different picture,
saying he was

03:56.536 --> 03:59.039 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
abusive, mentally unstable and
full of hate.

03:59.139 --> 04:04.044 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At the White House, President
Obama spoke
of his own concerns about such
individuals.

04:04.144 --> 04:06.113 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
One of the biggest challenges we
are going

04:06.213 --> 04:16.723 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
to have is this kind of
propaganda and perversions
of Islam that you see generated
on the Internet,

04:16.823 --> 04:24.064 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and the capacity for that to
seep into the
minds of troubled individuals.

04:24.164 --> 04:28.101 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Meanwhile,
police said today
they have identified nearly all
of the victims,

04:28.201 --> 04:33.707 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
among them, accountants,
baristas, hairdressers,
people, mostly young, who'd been
looking to

04:33.807 --> 04:36.843 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
unwind with a night of music and
dancing.

04:36.943 --> 04:41.715 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
With the city's wounds still
fresh, Orlando's
Mayor Buddy Dyer thanked the
city for its

04:41.815 --> 04:43.617 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
response.

04:43.717 --> 04:45.719 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BUDDY DYER, Mayor of Orlando,
Florida: We
will not be defined by the act
of a cowardly

04:45.819 --> 04:51.658 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
hater. We will be defined by how
we respond,
how we treat each other. And
this community

04:51.758 --> 04:53.660 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
has already stepped up to do
that.

04:53.760 --> 04:56.930 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: As the country
awaits the
latest developments in this
investigation,

04:57.030 --> 05:01.568 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a small army of volunteers here
in Orlando
have come to this community
center to do what

05:01.668 --> 05:03.503 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
they can to help out.

05:03.603 --> 05:08.341 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They loaded food and water today
at Orlando's
biggest LGBT community center,
just minutes

05:08.441 --> 05:13.246 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
from the site of the rampage.
Many said they
came to lend a hand, but also
just to be with

05:13.346 --> 05:15.215 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
others in mourning.

05:15.315 --> 05:18.685 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
COREY LYONS, President, Impulse
Orlando: It's
tragic. It's tragic across the
board. We saw

05:18.785 --> 05:23.890 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the act of what one person can
do, but in
the same day within 12 hours, we
saw the acts

05:23.990 --> 05:28.328 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of what many can do together to
really fight
this incident and really try to
come together.

05:28.428 --> 05:33.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRISTIE CRUZ, Volunteer: We're
all people,
and it just hurts cause it's
black, white,

05:33.366 --> 05:34.701 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
gay, no matter what. It doesn't
matter,

05:34.801 --> 05:36.536 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: It's an attack
on everybody.

05:36.636 --> 05:39.573 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRISTIE CRUZ: It's just -- yes,
we're all
people, we're all human, and we
-- it's just

05:39.673 --> 05:46.580 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
-- it's hard to deal with.
That's the thing
about the gay community, is, we
all know somebody

05:46.680 --> 05:51.218 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
who knows somebody who knows
somebody, because
this is a close group, and we're
-- it hurts

05:51.318 --> 05:53.119 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
us all.

05:53.220 --> 05:55.722 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: The shooting
happened as
Latin Night at the Pulse
nightclub was winding

05:55.822 --> 05:59.993 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
down, and a majority of the
victims identified
so far are Hispanic.

06:00.093 --> 06:02.429 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Christian Castelan is
Mexican-American and
gay.

06:02.529 --> 06:06.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRISTIAN CASTELAN, Volunteer: I
went out
to dinner last night with my
significant other

06:06.566 --> 06:12.739 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and other friends, and just
being closed to
him, that is even scary, after
what happened,

06:12.839 --> 06:17.077 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
because I was constantly just
looking around.
It just went from completely
comfortable to

06:17.177 --> 06:24.384 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
