matter of hours.
And it just continues to become
much more

06:24.484 --> 06:26.286 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
difficult than what it was
yesterday.

06:26.386 --> 06:32.359 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: A vigil is
being held later
tonight for the victims of the
shooting. It's

06:32.459 --> 06:36.429 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about less than a mile away from
the nightclub
where they lost their lives --
Gwen.

06:36.529 --> 06:41.034 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: William, I just
heard that young
man said to say to you that they
went from

06:41.134 --> 06:46.439 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
being comfortable to terrified
so quickly.
Is it fair to say that the
community is still

06:46.539 --> 06:48.241 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in a state of shock tonight?

06:48.341 --> 06:53.113 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Absolutely. I
mean, the
sense here is that this, like so
many other

06:53.213 --> 06:57.050 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
communities that have
experienced this type
of a tragedy, the sense of
safety that they

06:57.150 --> 06:58.985 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
had has been snatched away from
them.

06:59.085 --> 07:02.656 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that's something we heard
not just from
the gay community, but largely
in that community

07:02.756 --> 07:04.557 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
here, all over Orlando.

07:04.658 --> 07:09.462 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: So, William, is
there a special
impact in the gay -- if this was
Latin night

07:09.562 --> 07:14.067 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
at a gay nightclub, a special
impact in the
gay and lesbian community?

07:14.167 --> 07:15.902 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: It was,
absolutely.

07:16.002 --> 07:21.207 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I mean, the Latino community, as
we know,
it's largely a conservative
community. And

07:21.308 --> 07:26.479 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
being gay in the Latino
community is not as
easy as it might be, say, in the
white community.

07:26.579 --> 07:30.583 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And a lot of people mentioned to
me that there
might be the possibility that
people who were

07:30.684 --> 07:34.521 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
shot, people who might have been
killed or
wounded in this event might not
have been

07:34.621 --> 07:36.523 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
