07:36.623 --> 07:39.959 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so now they are forced to
have this conversation
that maybe they weren't ready to
be having,

07:40.060 --> 07:43.196 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that, oh, I was at this club
when this happened.

07:43.296 --> 07:48.802 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It just raised one more level of
a very, very
uncomfortable conversation for
them at a time

07:48.902 --> 07:51.004 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of this awful tragedy going on
here.

07:51.104 --> 07:56.576 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: And is there
evidence now of heightened
security around, in and around
Orlando, but

07:56.676 --> 07:58.645 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
especially in that neighborhood?

07:58.745 --> 08:03.883 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Absolutely. We
spent a good
deal of time today and yesterday
at that community

08:03.983 --> 08:05.785 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
center.

08:05.885 --> 08:09.289 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And now even there every time
they don't let
people stand outside, for fear
of drive-by

08:09.389 --> 08:13.259 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
shootings. They are checking
bags everywhere
they go. How much of that lasts
after this

08:13.360 --> 08:16.863 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
event dies down and people start
to go on
with their lives, we don't know.
But there

08:16.963 --> 08:19.099 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
is a very strong sense of
security here everywhere.

08:19.199 --> 08:22.502 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: William, thank so
much. We will
hear from you again tomorrow
night.

08:22.602 --> 08:25.305 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: All right,
good night, Gwen.

08:25.405 --> 08:30.577 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And some
perspective now on
how intelligence and law
enforcement agencies

08:30.677 --> 08:34.381 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
try to find and stop people like
the Orlando
killer.

08:34.481 --> 08:40.487 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
We turn to two men with
extensive experience
in counterterrorism operations
and investigations.

08:40.587 --> 08:46.493 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Michael Leiter was the director
the National
Counterterrorism center from
2007 to 2011,

08:46.593 --> 08:54.167 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
during both the George W. Bush
and Obama administrations.
And Ali Soufan was a supervisory
special agent

08:54.267 --> 08:59.706 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
with the FBI, where he worked on
both domestic
and international terrorism
investigations.

08:59.806 --> 09:03.810 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He now runs a security and
intelligence consulting
business.

09:03.910 --> 09:06.746 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And we welcome both of you to
the program.

09:06.846 --> 09:11.951 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Michael Leiter, to you first.
Based on everything
you know, how do you assess the
job that the

09:12.051 --> 09:18.858 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
FBI and other government
agencies did in looking
into what they heard about Omar
Mateen?

09:18.958 --> 09:20.260 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL LEITER, Former Director,
National
Counterterrorism Center: Well,
let's start

09:20.360 --> 09:22.462 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
with the premise that this is a
very hard
job.

09:22.562 --> 09:26.099 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As Jim Comey said today, they
not only have
to find needles in a haystack.
They have to

09:26.199 --> 09:31.104 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
predict which pieces of the way
ill eventually
become needles. I think what
Director Comey

09:31.204 --> 09:37.677 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
said was that they did a fair
amount of information
of this individual in 2014, to
include running

09:37.777 --> 09:41.614 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
operatives against him, doing
surveillance,
doing electronic surveillance.

09:41.714 --> 09:46.419 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And all of that led them to
conclude that
this wasn't a threat. And that
really suggests

09:46.519 --> 09:51.057 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
