What would that
have involved?

10:09.242 --> 10:13.680 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
ALI SOUFAN, Former FBI
Interrogator: Well,
I think we heard from Director
Comey that

10:13.780 --> 10:18.718 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
